keep your html css and js files inside public folder to use it with express static.
keep you html file name as index and ntg else.
index is default homepage

you have to serve index.html from public with express middlewere. 
you can include js script tag in hbs file. 

partials are set using hbs.setPartials(folder path of partials)

all hbs should be inside views folder. set view-engine to hbs.  